Superbia and Invidia were like,
a hair-trigger away from full-blown
warfare, right?

rows.label: tlk41300011_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Well I'm glad it never amounted to
anything in the end.

rows.label: tlk41300011_03_msg0003
rows.name:
I guess we can thank the Pope for
defusing the situation there.

rows.label: tlk41300011_03_msg0004

If war had broken out, I'd probably
have had to go back to Gula and
fight for Superbia.
